    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh. Suspension geometry remains true with updated bushings, ensuring the chassis handles high-G cornering with precision. An honest, performance-oriented example for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical integrity and visceral feedback.",
