    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though I want to be transparent about a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, shallow scuff on the rear passenger door that is only visible in direct sunlight. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no curb rash. Inside, the cabin is clean and smells fresh; the leather upholstery is soft and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and sunroof, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection performed just 200 miles ago. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced last year. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. Included are two sets of keys and a thick folder of service receipts. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been primarily garaged.",
